    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's almost midnight here so the doctor's office is closed. i just need to get through the night without this headache being unbearable. i don't have any bleeding or anything, just the headache. if i just take a single standard dose of ibuprofen, like one 200mg pill, is it really going to cause a huge problem? it's just one pill, surely that's fine?",
